Check to see if the lien request has been approved and processed.
condition ()

Form Statuses – Waiting for supervisor approval, Request Approved, and Request Denied
Finance Statuses – Pending, Accepted, and Revision Needed
Memo Statuses – matches Finance Status; set in workflow; 


If the lien request has been approved and processed, send an email to the finance team requesting approval for the loan.

Wait for a response from the finance team. (wait for approval) 
If the finance team approves the loan, send an email to the borrower notifying them of the approval.
If the finance team declines the loan, send an email to the borrower notifying them of the denial.
